{"tid":1813952,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[口罩] 搵到好野，我財經台巴打益各位財經台巴絲","createTime":"2020-01-06T15:35:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T04:09:51.000Z","uid":61161,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"64a2a0b6e89303f5a21455f9b50c15c37ba8c919","tid":1813952,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T15:35:34.000Z","msg":"利申：非打手Post，我都係第一次試用呢款，有錯/差唔好屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說追開口罩Post, 不外乎都係手術口罩/N95 8210(v)/其他不盡錄，但有啲人話有啲地方已經搵唔到口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n都有巴打推介呢款，咁岩比我搵到呢間榮光醫業賣呢款&ldquo;NASK 納米纖維智能殺菌口罩&rdquo;，仲要係由香港研發、設計及生產，獲 NIOSH N99 級別認証<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mscMsrS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmscMsrS.jpg&h=3335901d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但佢個新年優惠：<br />\n原價 $990（50個／盒），現優惠價 $600/盒<br />\n優惠期由即日至 2020年1月10日，圍返起$12一個，即棄罩一個戴到24小時<br />\n<br />\n比較返N95 $140-$160一盒20個，圍起$7-8一個，差唔多喇，睇自己負擔能力，再唔係就外科口罩，總知唔好唔戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一齊全民蒙面<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1521726444781208/posts/2623675034586338/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1521726444781208%2Fposts%2F2623675034586338%2F&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDUkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=cc2406db\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1521726444781208/posts/2623675034586338/</a>"},{"pid":"c7a1a6f066e33e1373aebeec77cd79bc5f9b1260","tid":1813952,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T03:59:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1521726444781208/posts/2629382150682293/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1521726444781208%2Fposts%2F2629382150682293%2F&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1Nr